The paper discusses the use of neural networks for autonomous robot navigation, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques such as convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) and recurrent neural networks (cs.LG) for memory architectures. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of reinforcement learning (cs.AI) for training the neural networks and the integration of the neural network with the robot's control system (cs.SY).
